1 17.20. "Supplier" means an alcoholic beverage manufacturer, importer, marketer, or
2 wholesaler selling alcoholic beverages to a wholesaler licensed in this state for
3 purposes of resale.
4 18.21. "Tribal licensee" means a person issued a local license by the governing body of a
