1 c. A manufacturing distillery may not engage in any wholesaling activities. Except
2 as provided by section 5-01-19.1, all sales and deliveries of spirits to any other
3 retail licensed premises in this state may be made only through a licensed North
4 Dakota liquor wholesaler. However, a manufacturing distillery may sell distilled
5 spirits to a domestic winery if the distilled spirits were produced from products
6 provided to the manufacturing distillery by the domestic winery.
